These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, snowmobile, van, boat
5 different games are played: billiard, chess, snooker, backgammon, canasta
City: hamburg, edinburgh, berlin, hannover, paris
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, prince, bongani, tiparillo, pall-mall
 1. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is the person driving the boat##1
 3. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 4. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person playing chess is the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 8. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person playing chess##1
10. the person driving the van is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is the dunhill-smoker##1
12. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Transport         | helicopter  | airplane    | van | snowmobile    | boat  |
| Game   | chess  | billiard | snooker | backgammon | canasta  |
| City           | hamburg     | paris     | hannover  | edinburgh   | berlin    |
| Cigar         | bongani | tiparillo    | prince | dunhill  | pall-mall |

