.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different games are played: domino, backgammon, chess, monopoly, go
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda, lemonade, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
City: venice, prague, berlin, colone, london
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, sudoku, fishing, puzzles, dancing
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person traveling to prague##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 8. the person playing chess is the person traveling to berlin##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person playing chess##1
10. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
11. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
12. the person playing chess is the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Game          | chess        | go | backgammon     | monopoly      | domino  |
| Beverage           | mirinda   | lemonade | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk | fanta |
| City   | berlin | colone     | london | venice    | prague  |
| Hobby   | puzzles     | sudoku | hiking    | dancing      | fishing    |

