.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, mechaniccher, chef, mechanic, bartender
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, designersy, western, time-travel, comedy
There 5 different types of food: cranberry, orange, plum, cucumber, bartendermelon
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: classical, reggae, metal, gospel, pop
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person eating bartendermelon##1
 2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person eating cranberry is in the middle##1
 4. the mechaniccher is in the middle##1
 5. the person eating plum is on the far right##1
 6. the person watching designersy movies is on the far left##1
 7. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
10. the fan of metal is on the right of the person eating orange##1
11. the person eating plum is the person watching zombie movies##1
12. the bartender is on the right of the designer##1
13. the mechanic is the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Job      | mechanic          | chef  | mechaniccher       | designer     | bartender      |
| Movie-Genre         | designersy | comedy | time-travel  | western   | zombie    |
| Food   | orange        | bartendermelon | cranberry | cucumber    | plum   |
| Music-Genre     | classical   | metal | pop      | reggae | gospel |

