.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, handball, snowboarding, baseball, water-polo
5 different pets are kept: bird, hamster, goat, dog, turtle
5 different games are played: chess, poker, monopoly, go, billiard
The people have 5 different hobbies: sudoku, cooking, hiking, woodworking, singing
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person playing poker is the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the person playing chess is the owner of the bird##1
 5. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person playing go##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is in the middle##1
 9. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person playing monopoly##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Sport          | baseball        | climbing       | snowboarding | handball   | water-polo  |
| Pet   | turtle | goat | hamster | bird   | dog |
| Game   | go         | billiard     | poker | chess | monopoly     |
| Hobby     | sudoku        | cooking        | singing    | woodworking    | hiking      |

