 7. the prince-smoker is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 8. the montecristo-smoker is in the middle##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1
11. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
12. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
