The people use 5 different means of transport: roller, bus, tram, motorbike, car
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, august, march, december, september
 1. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who growsazalea is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person eating lettuce is on the far left##1
10. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person driving the car##1
11. the person eating grapefruit is in the middle##1
12. the person who's birthday is in december is the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Food         | lettuce  | pepper  | grapefruit    | strawberry | cranberry |
| Flower   | marigold        | orchid  | azalea | balloon-flower      | daffodil        |
