 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of classical##1
 5. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of blues is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 7. the fan of country is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the fan of blues is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person watching mystery movies##1
12. the person traveling to prague is the fan of ambient##1
13. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

