.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-8::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, skateboard, quad-bike, snowmobile, van
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, blood-red, red, brown, black
The people have 5 different hobbies: reading, traveling, hiking, magic-tricks, cooking
The people have 5 different jobs:  engineer, scientist, librarian, journalist, security-guard
 1. the engineer is the person driving the train##1
 2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 3. the engineer is on the far left##1
 4. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
 8. the scientist is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person who likes red is the librarian##1
10. the person who likes black is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who likes black##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
13. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the librarian##1
14. the security-guard is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
| Transport      | train        | snowmobile   | skateboard  | quad-bike         | van |
