.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, skydiving, chess, photography, puzzles
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, february, january, november, may
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, swimming, water-polo, sailing, surfing
There 5 different types of food: mango, cabbage, broccoli, peas, kale
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person eating kale##1
 6. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is the person eating mango##1
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
11. the person eating peas is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's sport is sailing##1
13. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Hobby      | camping      | skydiving       | puzzles         | photography  | chess |
| Birthday   | january  | november | february | october  | may  |
| Sport   | sailing    | swimming    | cricket        | surfing | water-polo     |
| Food           | cabbage | broccoli      | mango       | peas   | kale   |

