.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: van, car, subway, boat, ship
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: marigold, daffodil, bellflower, sunflower, aconite
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, july, october, january, april
There are 5 different favourite colors: brown, fuchsia, lavender, apricot, azure
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person driving the car is the person who likes brown##1
 8. the person driving the subway is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who growsaconite##1
11. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
12. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
13. the person driving the boat is the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Transport   | car      | boat | subway  | ship    | van |
| Flower   | sunflower     | aconite     | daffodil | marigold      | bellflower      |
| Birthday           | october       | december     | july     | april     | january   |
| Color         | brown | apricot | fuchsia  | azure | lavender   |

