.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: reading, sudoku, skydiving, writing, photography
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: sports, adventure, horror, crime, animation
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, basketball, surfing, biathlon
House: palace, victorian, townhouse, colonial, art-deco
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the art-deco house is on the right of the victorian house##1
 3. the person watching animation movies is the palace house##1
 4. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
 5. the victorian house is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 6. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 8. the art-deco house is on the left of the palace house##1
 9. the palace house is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the art-deco house##1
12. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is photography##1
13. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| Hobby      | skydiving | photography    | sudoku   | writing   | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | horror   | animation | crime | adventure  |
| Sport           | handball     | surfing | basketball   | biathlon | lacrosse   |
| House     | victorian  | art-deco   | palace    | colonial   | townhouse |

