.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, guinea-pig, hamster, ferret, bird
There are 5 different favourite colors: emerald, purple, light-blue, apricot, ivory
5 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, whist, chess, scrabble
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, game, vegafina, chaman, oliveros
 1. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes apricot is the prince-smoker##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1
 6. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the person who likes light-blue is the person playing billiard##1
 8. the game-smoker is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1
11. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes ivory is in the middle##1
13. the person playing monopoly is the owner of the ferret##1
14. the person playing chess is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Pet      | guinea-pig | ferret   | hamster    | rabbit       | bird |
| Color   | light-blue           | purple   | ivory   | apricot       | emerald  |
| Game   | billiard       | monopoly | whist | chess     | scrabble   |
| Cigar     | vegafina    | game   | chaman   | prince | oliveros   |

 